latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Your wings were ready but our hearts were not 🥺

Its been a week today and I cannot sink in what has happened 😩
.
To my baby in heaven this is for you❤️😢

Life will never be the same again.
This was not your time to leave. 
Thank you for all the unconditional love & support you gave us all these 5years.

~
The way he left us has broken us completely, due to ignorance and unprofessional behaviour of the doctors we lost our baby & it’s something we can never take out of our heads.

The days have been so hard. Harder than I could ever imagine. All his belongings are everywhere and I cannot move them yet. His smell has comforted me I still cant believe he’s gone. He’s not here, I cant give him another kiss or pat😩

Keep him in your prayers🙏🏻😭

#myforeverlove #mybaby #frenchbulldog 
Song : Back Together Again- Alexandria Corn

MY FIRST EVER MUSIC ALBUM IS OUT NOW 🥹❤️

Wild Buffaloes Music ( @wildbuffaloesmusic ) presents, ‘Meet’, a young soulful track, sung by Aakash Sharma ( @aakash_sharrma ) and composed by Avneet ( @avneet.music ).

This uplifting song features Aakash, a young singer who moves to Mumbai against his father’s will, to achieve his dream of becoming a singer.
His childhood friend, Divya ( @divyamohite_ ) supports him in his decision which brings him an unexpected opportunity changing his life forever!

Happy Mother's Day, Ma💕

Thank you for tolerating me on my worst days and believing in me on the days I didn’t believe in myself. You’re the best thing that ever happened to me. Thank you for everything, Ma🥺
From moving mountains, for giving endlessly, for being my everything. I hope I can give back even half of what you’ve given me. I’m trying, and I always will.

I love you so much 🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿

From spontaneous plans to unforgettable memories — a whirlwind escape with Mom and my brother through the magic of Mussoorie, the peace of Rishikesh, and the spirit of Haridwar. 

Uttarakhand, you surprised us in the best way✨️
